function initSort(){$("#listWithHandle").sortable({stop:function(){var n=$(this).sortable("serialize");sortFavourites(n)}})}function sortFavourites(n){$.ajax({data:n,type:"POST",url:Urls.SortFavouritePages,success:function(n){n.isSuccess?(showSuccessAlert(n.message),listFavourites()):showAlert(n.message)},error:function(){showAlertWithGeneralErrorMessage()}})}function listFavourites(){$.ajax({url:Urls.FavouritePagesPartial,contentType:"application/html; charset=utf-8",type:"GET",dataType:"html"}).success(function(n){$("#favouritesDiv").html(n);initSort()}).error(function(n,t){showAlert(t)})}function deleteFavouriteOnPage(n){Swal.fire({title:"Emin misiniz?",text:"Bu kayıt kalıcı olarak silinecektir!",icon:"warning",showCancelButton:!0,confirmButtonColor:"#c70039",cancelButtonColor:"#6c757d",confirmButtonText:"Sil",cancelButtonText:"Vazgeç"}).then(t=>{t.value&&$.ajax({dataType:"json",type:"POST",url:Urls.DeleteFavouritePage,data:{id:n},success:function(n){n.isSuccess===!0?(showSuccessAlert(n.message),listFavourites()):n.message!==null?showAlert(n.message):showAlertWithGeneralErrorMessage()},error:function(){showAlertWithGeneralErrorMessage()}})})}$(document).ready(function(){initSort()});